title: 11/30: Mailbag! (Recorded Fri.) (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Special guest Jamey Eisenberg hops on the mailbag episode! We'll give you some of the NFL news (2:00) and talk about the NFL playoff picture. Who do we want to see make the playoffs in each conference? Then it's some DFS advice (9:15), your Apple Podcast questions (11:55), Fantasy Regulators (16:35), emails (23:00) and tweets (36:50). 
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
